d12b9158-c721-4456-bc2c-3bb30951f558.title: Note
d12b9158-c721-4456-bc2c-3bb30951f558.text: Missing after starting, woo can do for now

options.text: Any hints where I can find some treasure?
Hmm I'm not sure about that.

113b1d93-b763-4fab-9a3f-6d1de10ab071.title: <player>
113b1d93-b763-4fab-9a3f-6d1de10ab071.text: Any hints where I can find some treasure?

1e2c863d-0cda-4f14-a3bf-76ce1eabf461.title: Restless ghost
1e2c863d-0cda-4f14-a3bf-76ce1eabf461.text:
Wooooooo woo! Wooooo woo wooooo woowoowoo woo
Woo wooo. Wooooo woo woo? Woooooooooooooooooo!

options.text: Thank you. You've been very helpful.

074688ff-bebf-4a92-aa1f-ee02d1a77a5c.title: <player>
074688ff-bebf-4a92-aa1f-ee02d1a77a5c.text: Thank you. You've been very helpful.

options.text: My brother had EXACTLY the same problem.

811fb315-dfc6-4095-b368-33b0d5ce1757.title: <player>
811fb315-dfc6-4095-b368-33b0d5ce1757.text: My brother had EXACTLY the same problem.

options.text: You'll have to give me the recipe some time...

d0a8259e-f5e0-42a4-9183-61394698dfee.title: <player>
d0a8259e-f5e0-42a4-9183-61394698dfee.text: Hmm... I'm not so sure about that.

e7b857ef-068d-4908-87d0-50dfdb708fa2.title: <player>
e7b857ef-068d-4908-87d0-50dfdb708fa2.text: Ah well, better be off now...

5c54ac10-8ccb-4268-a56c-2e8153b46ea9.title: <player>
5c54ac10-8ccb-4268-a56c-2e8153b46ea9.text: You'll have to give me the recipe some time...

options.text: Hmm... I'm not so sure about that.

a9d24b90-2ff8-4289-89ba-f4527dfaefdc.title: Restless ghost
a9d24b90-2ff8-4289-89ba-f4527dfaefdc.text: Did you just understand what I said???

options.text: Yep, now tell me what the problem is.
No, you sound like you're speaking nonsense to me.

9a22d5c7-d2de-4e01-bd8d-167afead2756.title: Restless ghost
9a22d5c7-d2de-4e01-bd8d-167afead2756.text:
Oh! It's your amulet that's doing it! I did wonder. I
don't suppose you can help me? I don't like being a
ghost.

options.text: Yes, ok. Do you know why you're a ghost?

400bd137-7be7-4923-bc04-87bee72257b5.title: <player>
400bd137-7be7-4923-bc04-87bee72257b5.text: Yep, now tell me what the problem is.

f2f433d0-69ca-4705-97b5-312129ad418b.title: Restless ghost
f2f433d0-69ca-4705-97b5-312129ad418b.text:
WOW! This is INCREDIBLE! I didn't expect anyone
to ever understand me again!

1604dd7b-445b-4712-ae39-840367231106.title: <player>
1604dd7b-445b-4712-ae39-840367231106.text: Ok, Ok, I can understand you!

5a55d893-09fb-4435-bdbf-37fda7a59565.title: <player>
5a55d893-09fb-4435-bdbf-37fda7a59565.text:
But have you any idea WHY you're doomed to be a
ghost?

3f539b4d-31a9-4821-a7fc-a767ccd81ff3.title: Restless ghost
3f539b4d-31a9-4821-a7fc-a767ccd81ff3.text: Well, to be honest... I'm not sure.

12e3b7d1-6d5a-4f78-b7c1-2f5f156f7bb9.title: <player>
12e3b7d1-6d5a-4f78-b7c1-2f5f156f7bb9.text:
I've been told a certain task may need to be completed
so you can rest in peace.

e9809a79-63b4-4b31-b031-90b67f095d6a.title: Restless ghost
e9809a79-63b4-4b31-b031-90b67f095d6a.text:
I should think it is probably because a warlock has come
along and stolen my skull. If you look inside my coffin
there, you'll find my corpse without a head on it.

def235a8-bd1f-4ee9-b20e-f6d6edc402ee.title: <player>
def235a8-bd1f-4ee9-b20e-f6d6edc402ee.text: Do you know where this warlock might be now?

3ad87060-c34f-487a-8420-3b11f5f4f12a.title: Restless ghost
3ad87060-c34f-487a-8420-3b11f5f4f12a.text:
I think it was one of the warlocks who lives in the big
tower by the sea south-west from here.

c3df5b12-c0ab-4870-8a48-d2ffaf9230b2.title: <player>
c3df5b12-c0ab-4870-8a48-d2ffaf9230b2.text:
Ok. I will try and get the skull back for you, then you
can rest in peace.

1946d349-5f87-4f8c-a711-3a7328dbf955.title: Restless ghost
1946d349-5f87-4f8c-a711-3a7328dbf955.text: Ooh, thank you. That would be such a great relief!

cd1ecf21-9cb4-4db4-9b62-219805820977.title: Restless ghost
cd1ecf21-9cb4-4db4-9b62-219805820977.text: It is so dull being a ghost...

ba21e5dd-e298-47b3-be39-9689199faf73.title: <player>
ba21e5dd-e298-47b3-be39-9689199faf73.text: No, you sound like you're speaking nonsense to me.

71409648-8ae9-4fdd-af06-b458e6f59fe1.title: Restless ghost
71409648-8ae9-4fdd-af06-b458e6f59fe1.text: Oh that's a pity. You got my hopes up there.

3a44cc7b-ce7a-4487-9462-7a67560a01ca.title: <player>
3a44cc7b-ce7a-4487-9462-7a67560a01ca.text: Yeah, it is a pity. Sorry about that.

ad101093-4f4b-4381-98d1-234895f7ebc4.title: Restless ghost
ad101093-4f4b-4381-98d1-234895f7ebc4.text: Hang on a second... you CAN understand me!

d8cda1f9-d899-4746-b900-6c36f7dfe81b.title: Restless ghost
d8cda1f9-d899-4746-b900-6c36f7dfe81b.text: The first person I can speak to in ages...

3d0c97fe-1be6-4779-a490-beb59eea7101.title: Restless ghost
3d0c97fe-1be6-4779-a490-beb59eea7101.text:
I'm impressed. You must be very powerful. I don't
suppose you can stop me being a ghost?

options.text: Yes, ok. Do you know WHY you're a ghost?

2d44f4b8-d156-4449-90dc-e866ea7bdabd.title: <player>
2d44f4b8-d156-4449-90dc-e866ea7bdabd.text: Yes, ok. Do you know WHY you're a ghost?

9dc0a2a0-b5a3-4135-bff6-8a2e18f1c196.title: <player>
9dc0a2a0-b5a3-4135-bff6-8a2e18f1c196.text:
Nope. I just know I can't do much of anything like
this!

3805ff6a-666a-4c16-8a0d-470126f5d78f.title: Restless ghost
3805ff6a-666a-4c16-8a0d-470126f5d78f.text: How are you doing finding my skull?
